This is free and open source project for implement hospital system as easy way.
This is forked from https://sourceforge.net/p/ispirithalaya/wiki/Home/

Following function are included in the ispirityalaya.

    Online Doctor Channelling
    Online Payments (with out gate way)
    Chatting
    Online booking for checkup
    Booking time for labtest & checking whether the reports were ready
    Room reservations

Requirement.

Apache 2.2.x
Php 5.3.x
Mysql 5.1.x
Zend Freamworks 1.11.x (Zend lib and ZendX lib)

Features:
Simple Interfaces
Online Doctor Channeling
Online Payments (with out gate way)
Chatting
Online booking for checkup
Booking time for labtest & checking whether the reports were ready
Room reservations
Doctor Consultant.
Patient History Record Maintenance.
Staff Record Maintenance.

